<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Portfolio – Mathéo Pacheco-Corvo</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <!--
        PORTFOLIO COMPLET – MATHÉO PACHECO-CORVO
        - Fond clair avec touches de rouge
        - Animations avancées (transitions, parallax, glassmorphism, micro-interactions)
        - "IA" front-end qui scanne les sections et génère un résumé des grands titres
        - Code volontairement détaillé et riche pour un fichier "lourd"
    -->

    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-main: #f7f5fb;
            --bg-alt: #ffffff;
            --accent-red: #e53935;
            --accent-red-soft: #ff6f60;
            --accent-dark: #1f1b2e;
            --accent-muted: #8a8a9e;
            --accent-soft: #f0e9ff;
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            --border-soft: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 10, 40, 0.18);
            --shadow-soft-small: 0 10px 25px rgba(15, 10, 40, 0.12);
            --radius-large: 26px;
            --radius-medium: 18px;
            --radius-pill: 999px;
            --transition-fast: 0.25s ease-out;
            --transition-medium: 0.45s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1);
            --transition-slow: 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1);
            --font-main: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            --font-mono: "JetBrains Mono", "Fira Code", monospace;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-main);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #ffecec 0, #f7f5fb 40%, #ffffff 100%);
            color: var(--accent-dark);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Scrollbar custom */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 10px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #f0edf7;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent-red), var(--accent-red-soft));
            border-radius: 999px;
        }

        /* Layout principal */
        .page-wrapper {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        header {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 50;
            backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.92), rgba(255,255,255,0.85));
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
        }

        .nav-inner {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .brand-logo {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, #ffe3e0 0, #ffb3a7 30%, #e53935 70%, #b71c1c 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(229, 57, 53, 0.45);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .brand-logo::before,
        .brand-logo::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
            filter: blur(6px);
        }

        .brand-logo::before {
            width: 60%;
            height: 60%;
            top: -10%;
            left: 10%;
        }

        .brand-logo::after {
            width: 40%;
            height: 40%;
            bottom: -10%;
            right: 0;
        }

        .brand-text-main {
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .brand-text-sub {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 18px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--accent-dark);
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: color var(--transition-fast);
        }

        nav a::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            border-radius: inherit;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(229,57,53,0.18), transparent 60%);
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.8);
            transition: opacity var(--transition-fast), transform var(--transition-fast);
        }

        nav a:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: scale(1);
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-red);
        }

        .nav-cta {
            padding: 8px 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(229,57,53,0.4);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #ffe6e4);
            color: var(--accent-red);
            font-weight: 600;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(229,57,53,0.25);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform var(--transition-fast), box-shadow var(--transition-fast), background var(--transition-fast);
        }

        .nav-cta:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(229,57,53,0.35);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff5f4, #ffd1cc);
        }

        /* HERO SECTION */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px 60px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
            gap: 32px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero-left {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            border: 1px solid rgba(229,57,53,0.25);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft-small);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .hero-badge-dot {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, #ffebee 0, #e53935 60%, #b71c1c 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(229,57,53,0.18);
            animation: pulse-dot 1.8s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse-dot {
            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.25); opacity: 0.6; }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
            line-height: 1.15;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .hero-title span {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e53935, #ff7043);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
            max-width: 520px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero-highlight {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .hero-chip {
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .hero-chip-icon {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, #ffe0e0 0, #e53935 60%, #b71c1c 100%);
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: none;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e53935, #ff7043);
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 35px rgba(229,57,53,0.45);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            transition: transform var(--transition-medium), box-shadow var(--transition-medium), filter var(--transition-fast);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.01);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(229,57,53,0.6);
            filter: brightness(1.05);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            color: var(--accent-dark);
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(15,10,40,0.12);
            transition: transform var(--transition-fast), box-shadow var(--transition-fast), background var(--transition-fast);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(15,10,40,0.18);
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .hero-meta {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 18px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        .hero-meta-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2px;
        }

        .hero-meta-label {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
        }

        .hero-meta-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--accent-dark);
        }

        /* HERO RIGHT – CARD 3D */
        .hero-right {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            perspective: 1200px;
        }

        .hero-card {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-large);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #ffffff 0, #ffe6e4 40%, #f7f5fb 100%);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
            padding: 20px 20px 22px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transform-style: preserve-3d;
            transform: rotateY(-10deg) rotateX(6deg);
            animation: float-card 7s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes float-card {
            0% { transform: rotateY(-10deg) rotateX(6deg) translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: rotateY(-6deg) rotateX(4deg) translateY(-6px); }
            100% { transform: rotateY(-12deg) rotateX(7deg) translateY(0); }
        }

        .hero-card-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        .hero-card-title {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .hero-card-pill {
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(229,57,53,0.08);
            color: var(--accent-red);
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        }

        .hero-card-body {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1.2fr;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero-avatar {
            width: 110px;
            height: 110px;
            border-radius: 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffe6e4, #ffffff);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(15,10,40,0.25);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-avatar-inner {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 12px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                135deg,
                rgba(229,57,53,0.12),
                rgba(229,57,53,0.12) 6px,
                rgba(255,255,255,0.9) 6px,
                rgba(255,255,255,0.9) 12px
            );
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--accent-red);
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .hero-avatar-glow {
            position: absolute;
            inset: -40%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.9) 0, transparent 60%);
            opacity: 0.7;
            mix-blend-mode: screen;
        }

        .hero-card-info {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .hero-card-info h3 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .hero-card-info p {
            color: var(--accent-muted);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .hero-card-tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .hero-card-tag {
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            font-size: 0.7rem;
        }

        .hero-card-footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        .hero-card-kpi {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2px;
        }

        .hero-card-kpi span:first-child {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        }

        .hero-card-kpi span:last-child {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--accent-dark);
        }

        .hero-card-status {
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9, #ffffff);
            color: #2e7d32;
            border: 1px solid rgba(46,125,50,0.25);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .hero-card-orbit {
            position: absolute;
            inset: -40%;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px dashed rgba(229,57,53,0.25);
            pointer-events: none;
            animation: orbit-rotate 18s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes orbit-rotate {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .hero-card-orbit-dot {
            position: absolute;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, #ffe0e0 0, #e53935 60%, #b71c1c 100%);
            top: 10%;
            right: 18%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(229,57,53,0.18);
        }

        /* SECTION WRAPPER */
        main {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .section {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px 50px;
        }

        .section-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .section-title-block {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .section-kicker {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            color: var(--accent-red);
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
            max-width: 480px;
        }

        .section-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .section-pill {
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        /* GRID LAYOUTS */
        .grid-2 {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .grid-3 {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .grid-responsive {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
        }

        /* CARDS GÉNÉRALES */
        .card {
            border-radius: var(--radius-medium);
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft-small);
            padding: 16px 16px 18px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: -40%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(229,57,53,0.08), transparent 60%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity var(--transition-medium);
        }

        .card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .card-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .card-subtitle {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        .card-badge {
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(229,57,53,0.08);
            color: var(--accent-red);
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        }

        .card-body {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--accent-dark);
        }

        .card-footer {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .card-tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .card-tag {
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            font-size: 0.7rem;
        }

        /* SECTION COORDONNÉES + IA RESUME */
        .contact-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .contact-block {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .contact-item {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 4px;
        }

        .contact-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        .contact-value {
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .contact-note {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        .ai-panel {
            border-radius: var(--radius-medium);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #ffffff 0, #ffe6e4 40%, #f7f5fb 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(229,57,53,0.25);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
            padding: 16px 16px 18px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .ai-panel-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .ai-panel-title {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .ai-dot {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, #ffebee 0, #e53935 60%, #b71c1c 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(229,57,53,0.18);
            animation: pulse-dot 1.8s infinite;
        }

        .ai-panel-status {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        .ai-panel-body {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--accent-dark);
            max-height: 220px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding-right: 4px;
        }

        .ai-summary-item {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding: 6px 8px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
        }

        .ai-summary-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .ai-summary-text {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        .ai-panel-footer {
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        .ai-btn {
            padding: 6px 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: none;
            background: rgba(229,57,53,0.1);
            color: var(--accent-red);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            transition: background var(--transition-fast), transform var(--transition-fast);
        }

        .ai-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(229,57,53,0.18);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        /* COMPÉTENCES & QUALITÉS */
        .pill-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .pill {
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .pill-dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, #ffe0e0 0, #e53935 60%, #b71c1c 100%);
        }

        .lang-list {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .lang-item {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .lang-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .lang-level {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        /* LOISIRS */
        .hobby-list {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .hobby-item {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .hobby-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .hobby-text {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        /* FORMATIONS – TIMELINE */
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 18px;
        }

        .timeline::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: 6px;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(229,57,53,0.4), rgba(229,57,53,0.05));
        }

        .timeline-item {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .timeline-dot {
            position: absolute;
            left: -2px;
            top: 4px;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, #ffe0e0 0, #e53935 60%, #b71c1c 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(229,57,53,0.18);
        }

        .timeline-title {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .timeline-sub {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        .timeline-meta {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        /* EXPÉRIENCES – CARDS AVANCÉES */
        .exp-card {
            border-radius: var(--radius-medium);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.96);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft-small);
            padding: 14px 14px 16px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .exp-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: -40%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(229,57,53,0.08), transparent 60%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity var(--transition-medium);
        }

        .exp-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .exp-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .exp-title {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .exp-company {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        .exp-date {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }

        .exp-body {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-dark);
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .exp-body ul {
            padding-left: 16px;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .exp-body li {
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }

        .exp-footer {
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .exp-tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .exp-tag {
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            font-size: 0.7rem;
        }

        /* SECTION LETTRE DE MOTIVATION – PANEL LECTURE */
        .letter-panel {
            border-radius: var(--radius-large);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #ffffff 0, #ffe6e4 40%, #f7f5fb 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(229,57,53,0.25);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
            padding: 18px 18px 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .letter-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .letter-title {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .letter-meta {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        .letter-body {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--accent-dark);
            max-height: 260px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding-right: 4px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .letter-body p {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .letter-footer {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .letter-btn {
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: none;
            background: rgba(229,57,53,0.1);
            color: var(--accent-red);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            transition: background var(--transition-fast), transform var(--transition-fast);
        }

        .letter-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(229,57,53,0.18);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        /* SECTION CONTACT FINAL */
        .contact-final {
            border-radius: var(--radius-large);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #ffe6e4);
            border: 1px solid rgba(229,57,53,0.25);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
            padding: 18px 18px 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
            gap: 18px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .contact-final-text {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .contact-final-text h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .contact-final-text p {
            color: var(--accent-muted);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .contact-final-actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .contact-final-meta {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
        }

        .contact-final-form {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.96);
            border-radius: var(--radius-medium);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            padding: 12px 12px 14px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft-small);
        }

        .contact-final-form label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .contact-final-form input,
        .contact-final-form textarea {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            padding: 8px 10px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-family: var(--font-main);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color var(--transition-fast), box-shadow var(--transition-fast), background var(--transition-fast);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.96);
        }

        .contact-final-form input:focus,
        .contact-final-form textarea:focus {
            border-color: rgba(229,57,53,0.6);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(229,57,53,0.3);
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .contact-final-form textarea {
            min-height: 80px;
            resize: vertical;
        }

        .contact-final-form button {
            padding: 8px 14px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: none;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e53935, #ff7043);
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(229,57,53,0.45);
            transition: transform var(--transition-medium), box-shadow var(--transition-medium), filter var(--transition-fast);
        }

        .contact-final-form button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(229,57,53,0.6);
            filter: brightness(1.05);
        }

        /* FOOTER */
        footer {
            padding: 18px 20px 24px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent-muted);
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer span {
            color: var(--accent-red);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* ANIMATIONS D’APPARITION */
        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(18px);
            transition: opacity var(--transition-slow), transform var(--transition-slow);
        }

        .reveal.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* RESPONSIVE */
        @media (max-width: 960px) {
            .hero {
                grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
            }
            .hero-right {
                order: -1;
            }
            .contact-grid {
                grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
            }
            .contact-final {
                grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 720px) {
            .nav-inner {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }
            nav ul {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: flex-end;
            }
            .hero {
                padding-top: 24px;
            }
            .section {
                padding-top: 30px;
                padding-bottom: 36px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 520px) {
            .hero-card {
                transform: none;
                animation: none;
            }
            .hero-card-body {
                grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
            }
            .contact-block {
                grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
